✨My 2023 highlights ✨(read caption) 

1. My first celebrity interview with artist/celeb @anitta along with @fcbarcelona played on behave of @spotify <3 

2. I graduated with a BA from SDSU in May after 4 years of college😎

3. I moved to LA with the hope of pursuing content creation & it’s been one of the best decisions I have made!🙏🏽

4. I hit 500k on YouTube & got to celebrate with my 2 biggest supports, my mom & dad! ❤️

5. I attended my first pride event ever with two iconic creators that I have looked up too for a long time! 🏳️‍🌈

6. I got to film a YouTube video with the king of YouTube! @airrack 👑✨

7. I had a housewarming party that many creators came to when I moved to LA and they welcomed me with open arms. I will never forget this night.✨

8. I did a little pivot on social media, focusing a little bit more on fashion and highlighting my personality more and it’s been so fun and I’m so excited to share more with you all! 👟

9. I attended first streamys ever, and I got to meet so many creators that I watched as a teen on behalf of @youtube 📸 

10. Lastly, this year I focused on my mental health and physical health. I did boxing for the first time this year along with weight lifting that I hope to continue in 2023 💪🏽

GRWM to go to the first ever TikTok Concert! Y’all it was amazing!! S/o to @tiktok for bringing me along!
